reviewText: Fantastic, great condition and arrived very quickly. Thanks so much
I'm an Aussie Cold Chisel/Jimmy Barnes fan...this is a fantastic live Chisel concert & excellent quality DVD. Highly recommend it. Barnsey rox!

This video is in PAL format and I have not yet been successful in transferring it to NTSC format, hence I have not yet viewed it.  This is more of a pain than I had originally envisioned, and I warn other potential purchasers to consider their resources before ordering a DVD in foreign printed format.
